fields.description:
{html}<div><p>The following <strong>app.js</strong> causes Android emulator to
crash in 1.0.0. Replacing <strong>Ti.Platform.name</strong> with a
simple string prevents the crash.</p>
<pre>
<code class="javascript"> var win1 = Titanium.UI.createWindow({  
    title:'Tab 1',
    backgroundColor:'#fff'
});

var label1 = Ti.UI.createLabel({
    title: Ti.platform.name
});

win1.add(label1);
win1.open();</code>
</pre></div>{html}
